@Meshkovs_Nikita Good morning, Nikita. Our apologies for such unpleasant situation with the vouchers.
If you had some extra costs due to our irregularity, please submit us all the receipts via this form: https://t.co/N04NoZd2An
Our team will review them and get back to you.

@GunaBaz Labdien, Guna.
Informācija šajā situācijā tiek ņemta no reisa plānotā (un ne aktuālā) grafika, atvainojamies par to un reisa kavēšanos.
Aicinām jaunāko informāciju par lidojumu statusu skatīt šeit: https://t.co/YkMzCDobpU

@DianaiD @Gatwick_Airport @riga_airport Hello and sorry to hear about this unpleasant situation, our apologies.
We kindly ask you to check this link for all your actions in this case: https://t.co/pDmf3gcMZN
Our teams are doing everything in order to locate the bags and deliver them as soon as possible.
